### 1. Register a New User
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ROLE_USER"
}

###

### 2. Login to Get JWT Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Attempt to Access Secured Endpoint without JWT (Should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects

###

### 4. Access Secured Endpoint with JWT Token (Replace {{token}} or use login response token)
# Replace the token below with the token received from step 2
GET http://localhost:8080/projects
Authorization: Bearer <paste_token_here>

###

### 5. Access H2 Console (Should be accessible/allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/h2-console